      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Founded in 2009 and has developed a loyal following of local and  international  clientele  through commitment to excellent service and maintaining a relaxing environment.Both our Spa Branches• Separate female and male treatment areas• VIP rooms for utter privacy• Spacious attached showers and modern restroom• Post-service drink selections• Genuine products from the USA and Korea (eg. OPI and Matrix)• An Ethical Code of Conduct for our staff and guestsOur vision is to be known as the leading mid-range spa in Batam. That is, we aim to have a reputation as an ethical day spa with the most outstanding service and environment at a sensible price.For further information about us, please visit www.spacentralbatam.com"
          }
        ]
      },
