                "text": "Welcome and Consultation:&nbsp;Upon arrival,&nbsp;you'll be greeted by the staff and may have a brief consultation to discuss your preferences and any areas you'd like to focus on.Preparation:&nbsp;You'll be provided with a locker,&nbsp;robe,&nbsp;and slippers to change into before your treatment.The Treatment:&nbsp;Enjoy your chosen treatments in a private room,&nbsp;experiencing a variety of techniques to promote relaxation and rejuvenation.Relaxation Time:&nbsp;Some packages may include time for relaxation after your treatments,&nbsp;allowing you to enjoy the calming atmosphere and sip on herbal tea."
